ygData.messageBody:
Are you referring to all the quest items for the crafted armor? I disagree... Griffon eyes, arnt for mid 20's, and the Werewolf talon from mistmoore castle is REALLY not for mid 20's :)

I think all quest items for the
armor are suited for mid 20s. (if you are a kiter, you
may be able to get them sooner).

Belgarth
